                        <persName ref="http://viaf.org/viaf/90068840" type="aut">Ibn al-Quffابن القف الكركي</persName>
                     </author>
                     <title xml:lang="ar" key="work_7757">شرح فصول أبقراط</title>
                     <title xml:lang="en" type="desc" key="work_7757">Commentary on Hippocratic Aphorisms</title>
                     <title xml:lang="en" type="alt" key="work_7757">Sharḥ Fuṣūl Abuqrāṭ</title>
                     <note>Original manuscript in the British Library</note>
                     <note>This is a lemmatically arranged commentary. The introduction begins on f. 1b; the beginning of each Book is as follows: Bk1: 2b; Bk2: 24a; Bk3: 72a; Bk4: 97a; Bk5: 131a; Bk6: 154a; Bk7: 167b.</note>
                     <listBibl>
                        <bibl>
